---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
	<section class="intro">
		<h1>Who am I?</h1>
		<p>
			I'm a curious builder exploring the intersection of technology and creativity.
			My work spans from crafting elegant code to experimenting with emerging AI capabilities,
			always with a focus on simplicity and purpose.
		</p>
		<p>
			This space serves as a digital garden where I cultivate ideas, document experiments,
			and share thoughts on technology, design, and the evolving landscape of human-computer interaction.
		</p>
		<p>
			I believe in the power of minimal design, thoughtful engineering, and the beauty of
			well-crafted systems that do one thing exceptionally well.
		</p>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.intro {
		max-width: 650px;
	}

	.intro h1 {
		color: var(--accent-color);
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.intro p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.intro p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
</style>
